"Swiss Youth in Science. One group had the task of finding a new policy "
"related to technology and ecology that will influence smart and sustainable "
"progress in the next 10 years. They decided to design a government funded, "
"NGO coordinated database that gives the consumer feedback on the ecology and "
"fairness of her/his consumption behavior through alerts in a smartphone "
"application. They chose to name the idea BuyAware."
msgstr ""
"BuyAware entsteht am Swiss Talent Forum, einem Think Tank organisiert von "
"Schweizer Jugend forscht. Eine Gruppe hatte die Aufgabe ein politisches "
